Just chillin in PC Support Class right now, finished my exam, I think I did pretty good, it wasn't terribly hard. BUt naywayz this weekend kinda sucked. We all went to the lyman tournament, in my opinion people did good, but there were hard ass people there, like kids that were 16th in the nation. WEll the worst thing happened also Joey broke his elbow. Things couldn't get any worse. We just lost our awesome 103 pounder. Hopefully he will be back by districts time. I didn't do too good at the tournament, but again it was really tough. Overall we came in 5th place, which isn't that bad considering there were such hard teams there. went to bed at 5:00 AM on sunday morning and didn't wake up till 2:00. I was dead tired, and I went to Wal Mart at 3:30 AM, I am friggin nuts. 
     Another plus is that Pat is getting his car back finally. That bitch is going to smoke all others. The REDLINE BOYZ are at it again.

Well tonight was an eventfull night, first off all we have to wrestle
Atlantic. Every year we wrestle atlantic we can beat them, and in the
paper they make it sound like they almost kicked our asses. Well 
I know I was tired of this bullshit, and so were a few other of my
teammates (Joe, Steven, Brian, Cory, Me, and a bunch others.) So
anywayz wqe all weigh in, everyone on weight. We step out onto the mat
and everyone gets out there and whoops ass in their match. Some should
have got a pin in their match, but as long as it's a win I am F***ing
happy. Then Onan(King of Stalling) gets on the mat and starts
wrestling, he is getting back points for friggin made up moves, I mean
what the hell. So then he insists on throwing his legs in on the kid.
He has no clue in the world how to use the legs. All it is for him is a
Fake Russian Stalling Tactic. Some Bullshit. Then Darron gets out there
and gets his first win, he stuck the kid. Then it was getting close to
my match so I started to warm up harder. Then Joey pinned his kid. It
was showtime, I was ready to get this shit going, I didn't care who
they sent out there, I as gonna whoop the shit out of them. They send
out this kid, and I shake his hand and start to wrestle pretty hard, I
hit a duck under, then I put in the legs ( cuz I have used them before,
unlike Onan), and I start hipping into the kid, and get him flat. But I
go outside the circle so I had to go from the Ref's position. Then this
kid does a stand up and I slam his ass, and he gets a point for me
slamming him. Then after that I pinned him in a Saturday Night Ride.
Congrats to Steven tonight too, he ankle picked the shit out of his
kid. Also Rhett did good tonight, even though he lsot, he still was a
better wrestler than Balboa, and he will beat him the next time he
see's him. Well that's about it for now, but all I can say is "THAT"S
HOW FLAGLER ROLL'S BITCHES" Duece Up, A-Town Stay Down

On Wed. we had a match against Deltona. There was a huge crowd at the gym. It was awesome. We absolutly demolished Deltona. So just when I think I want to quit wrestling beasue of cutting weight, I win, So I want to keep going. I went out on the mat with the intention of ripping my kid a new asshole. SERIOUSLY. I wasn't gonna ease up one bit .I finally get out on the mat after warming up for like 45 minutes. I shake the kids hand and absolutly go Buck Wild. I charge at the kid. BUt then I give him a bloody nose so he has to stop and get it all fixed up. Bt then in the first period I pin him in 1:24. The rest of the team also was awesome. We had some people that should have won their matches, but what can you do. All the practice, hardwork, and determination paid off. We Kicked Ass.
 On Firday we had a match against Titusville, this team was going to be a little better than Deltona. But they weren't goin to be a bunch of puss's either. So before the match caoch gives us his pep talk to get us all fired up. I was like "Hell Yea" Let's go out theere and kick someones ass. So we get warmed up in the room while JV is wrestling. I'm gettin pumped up and ready to go. We run out on to the mat, and get our warm up going. Me and Joey are warming up really hard. So Joey has to wrestle a girl. No big deal, she wants to wrestle, don't treat her any different. So this girl and the kid I am going to wrestle are watchin' me and him warm up. I am like shit they can watch all they want. We are gonna beat their asses. The time comes, I run out on the mat, just liek the last matchI bull rush the kid and kick his ass in 30 seconds or less, I don't know the exact time. But anywayz needless to say FPC Wrestling Kicked Ass once again. Great Job Guys.
FPC Wrestling 2-0  and on the way to the top.

Well.......A lot of stuff has been going on, between havin' the Greatest Most Wonderful Girlfriend ever, workin on Project REDLINE, school, and wrestling, there hasn't been a lot of time for writin' in the ol' LJ. But anywayz, school has been crazy. This is my first time taking a college class (for Duel Enrollment)and it has been pretty crazy, we write a lot of essays, but all in all it is a pretty fun class. Gettin ' pretty good grades this year, so I am happy about that. Now the famed Project REDLINE, well I think that is all l I have to say, well maybe not. It has been crazy every day gettin' in new parts and things to do to it. It will be the HOTTEST, BADDEST, SICKEST car on the streets. Everyone ready to have a challenge on ur hands, well don't be ready cuz it is gonna blow you outa the water. And just wait till christmas time (U will see what's gonna happen). All I want to do with Project REDLINE is find Mr. "Three Gears Man". This kid thinks he has the baddest car on the streets, and all he can say is "O man all I have is three gears in my car". Well let's think, why would you only have three gears, O prolly cuz u blew the other two u Ass. Anywayz that project is enoguh in it's own. Wrestling season just started and it is already gettin' kinda crazy. This Friday is the PreSeason Classic at 5:00 P.M., you all better be there. Wrestling practice isn't what I would say has been fun, but what the hell I can't complain it keeps me in shape. I finally got a new pair of wrestling shoes this year, they are friggin' pimp. Anywayz been hangin out with Nicole all the time. We haven't spent a whole weekend together in a while, but it's all good. She is so great I don't know how lucky I can get. First of all she is BEAUTIFUL, smart, funny, good sense of humor, I could go on for hours, but this livejournal doesn't need to go on for months now. Anywayz been hangin ' with the REDLINE BOYZ lately, doin' what we do. Me and Pat went to D-Town and picked up Halo-2, he played the shit out of that game. I can't wait till Need For Speed Underground 2 comes out, I will be playing that game like every damn day. Anywayz I am kinda tired and all, so I am gonna roll to bed and watch some TV. Duece Up.

Haven't updated in a while but anywayz........ This weekend was AWESOME... On Friday I went on a bike ride with Nicole......And then this dude rides by and drops his truck and like snaps his neck to loook back at Nicole....I mean I don't blame the guy, she is beautiful.......But then I was like  "Hey, she's only 12" LOL....Then we rode back to her house and her dad asked me if I wanted to come in for dinner.....SO I was like No Thank you..... But then I ended up going anywayz.......So we had dinner and a few interesting conversations.....And then we went back out on the bikes again...... I rode her back home and we talked for a lil' bit and then I rode back home.
 So on Saturday I woke up around 10:00 for some reason....Then I did a couple of things....then Nicole called and was like "Do you want the good news or the bad news" So I was like O damn...What now....She was like my friends want it to be a girls only day......So biggie tho.....Cuz I still got to come over for movies.......So then about 1:00 or so Pat came over, and we rolled over to Tara's house, cuz she wanted to see his new car. Then we came back to my house to chill for a lil'. I took a shower... Then I took a little spin in Pat's car, WOW that car is sick, it shifts so clean and simple....But the whole time I was drivin' there was like mass cops everywhere, so I was like OMG. But U know how a REDLINE BOY does it, they don't fear...... So then I came back home and Pat drove me over to Nicole's.......Then I cuddled up on the couch with Nicole and watched movies........So needless to say I had a good time.........But anywayz....I met Nicole's friend kaitlyn....She is def pretty chill...... And that "Third Season" LOL... Then I went outside at about 1:00 or so and talked to Nicole and gave her a good night kiss and left....that is def a long walk home..........DANG.....But anywayz that's eit for now...

Well today I get a call at about 9 from my g-pa, and then trent. And I am lookin outsie and it is raining, so that kills my whole day at the beahc.That was annoying. So then I go back to bed. And Trent shows up at like 11:00 and wakes me up. So I get outa bed and it's friggin' raining.....I was SOOOOOOOO pissed. Cuz I had my whole day planned out......I was gonna go chill at the beach with Nicole.....Then maybe see a movie later.......NOOOOOOO things never go the way I want them too. So I get to installin' stuff on Anthony's truck for him. I installed a set of Sony Xplod speakers in his car, and a set of tweeters too. Then after that I installed a set of Pioneer 6X8 inch speakers in Trents car. So me and Pat messed with Anthony's system to see what sounds best. So then we ordered some pizza. And worked on the system some more. Then I talked to Nicole for a little while. And then we finished up some stuff on his system. Trent went home and Anthony went to work. So I called Nicole to see whats up, and we talked for a little bit. Then I cleaned up a little and me and Pat and Goose went to Wal-Mart. So me and Pat leave Wal-Mart and go into the winn dixie parking lot to see if Jay is still working. So we past Bealls and a lady crosses the street and we go by. So this lady gets in her car with her husband and like 2 otha doods and rides up next to us talkin' crap, like "U Almost Ran Me Over" I was like yea what ever......Big Phat rain down on that. So we pull straight ahead and the car turns right. They try to take a U turn, but they see that we are rollin through to Perkins. So they go to Perkins and hop out their car and start yellin shit to us. SO Pat is like FINE CATCH ME BITCH.....and we took off......The stuff that happens to REDLINE BOYZ I'll Tell ya....So then we go back to Pat's house and Kailyn comes over. So then we come back to my house, and I start wiring my sound system up. Then Pat and Marcus and Kailyn leave...... So I finish my wiring and then start cleaning up..... Then I went and took a shower and came out and talked to goose for a lil online....Now I am here rightin' this......Well it was a bad day in the sense that I didn't get to hang out with Nicole........But a good day in the sense that I finshed a lot of stuff on Anthony's and Trent's cars.......So anywayz the day def would have been betetr if I coulda gone to the beahc with Nicole and chilled and done some skimboarding.... But things never turn out like I want them to sao w/e.....ttyl

So on Thursday, I wake up at like 7:30. I call Pat and see whats up. Then Pat came by and we ate breakfast. Then we went to Wal-Mart to meet Czar,Amber,Kristy,Goose,and Chris. Then we all pile into Czar's van and roll to Wet n' Wild for the day. So we get there, and all get in and start goin' on some rides. Let me tell yo, I HAVE NEVER SEEN SO MANY FAT PEOPLE IN MY LIFE......Do people look in the mirror before the put on a bathing suit. So we all have some lunch and go on some more slides n stuff.....Then we all head back to the van and go to the gas station o we can get some slurpees and some food. Then we get goin' home. So we all take a PHAT nap in the car. So when I wake up we are pulling into the Wal-Mart parking lot. Then Pat dropped me off at my house, and I came inside and was gettin ready to go to sleep and Trent calls. So I talk to him for a lil', cuz he is coming over. So I get up and he gets here with Anthony. So I Install his Intake in his Explorer. As I am installing the Intake, Pat comes over. So I finish the Intake, and that thing is BEAUTIFUL. So we start lookin' at Anthony's Sound system, cuz it isn't working. So u know how the REDLINE BOYZ can fix anything. So Pat figures out that it is the fuse. So Anthony's Wiring is so jerry rigged it isn't even funny. So everybody leaves and I come inside and eat dinner. Then about 20 mins after dinner is over. Anthony and Trent come back. Then Pat came back over with Jay. So me, Pat, and Jay dig into Anthony's system. This kid had enough wire in his car that he was gettin' yesterdays radio stations. LOL. So we start putting his system together the right way.  Then my mom tells me that his bass is  too loud and to  turn it down. Then we start to drive around and figure out tuning the amp. We park in the circle at the end of the street and some dude comes outa the woods and is like "Excuse me, can u please turn that down, ur rattling the windows in my house." This dood lives 2 streets away.LOL. So we drive around and fix it and come home. His shit is loud. Then we put it all back together and he rolled out. So did Pat and Jay. Then I talked to Nicole for awhile, like until 2:15.
Today I woke up at like 11:45, I woke up to Pat's Bass rollin' down the street. LOL. So we chilled for a lil and he rolled out. Then Trent came over. And we chilled. Then he brought a friend over. We went up to Wal-Mart to get some stuff to install his strobes. So then I started installin' his strobes and then Pat came over and showed us his Air Soft gun. I pelted Trent with it about 10 times. It was sooooo funy... I hit him in his finger......Then I kept on installin' his strobes. Then Pat left to go to the movies. then the pizza guy came and gave us the pizza and we talked to him for like 10 mins. Then we ate. And I go on the computer and talked to Nicole for a little bit. Then I finished installin his strobes. Then he left, and dropped off his friend. Then I finished cleaning the garage. And now I am talking to Nicole........So I am gonna go now.........

Today was such a crazy day......This morning Pat calls the house at about 11:00, so after that I go back to sleep for a lil and wake up....Pat came over and we were gonna put tweeters in his car, but we decided not to. So then we rolled over to Chris's house so we could wash the cars. We washed the cars and went back to the house and Pat dropped me off. So then I came online and talked to Nicole for a lil' bit. So then I figure I would go on the daily bike ride a little late today. So on the bike ride i pass Goose and Chris, so I go and talk to them for a lil bit and then continue ridin'. So I did my normal loop for biking, and was coming back. Then I pass Goose again and I told him to pull over on the other street so i could talk to him. So he tell me that e is going to go to dinner for a church thing and he asks me if I wanna go. So he says ride back to ur house and put on a shirt and lets go. So I just start BOOKIN', I am doin like 30 MPH ( seriously) , and I get half way down the street and SUDDENLY my chain slips and I lost my footing and one foot hits the ground and the other gets caught. So my whole body lunges to the front of the bike and the bike does like a tail whip and I do a front flip with the bike and SMACK MY HEAD ON THE GROUND. So then I am like HOLY SHIT, so Goose pulls over and sees if I am ok n stuff. I got road rash on my back and elbow and prolly got a concusion. My head go a lil road rash too. So then we go back to the house and bandage me up and roll over to get some dinner. From there we went to the Russles house to have cake and icecream and go swimming and stuff. So then after everybody leaves we all go up stairs. So we chill and watch Dumb and Dumber and talk n stuff, play some pool. Then Pat took Jay and Ashley home, and then brought me home. Today was crazy, I can't beleive what happened on my bike, IT HURT SO BAD. But U know what I did??? I HOPPED RIGHT UP AND KEPT ON GOIN'. DO U KNOW WHY? CUZ I'M A REDLINE BOY, AND I CAN DUST IT OFF.

But anywayz.....We talked for a lil bit and I had to go take a shower and we went crusin' round Daytona...... And we went to 600 North as it was gettin' out and I saw Megan,Cordelia,Kayla, U know their whole crew there, I saw Chad Buxman and afew othas too. Then we wen to the waffle house and got something to eat and came home and played some CRAZY Texas Hold' EM'.... Then today we woke up and I went to the volunteer thing again....Like all day......Then I came home and cleaned my room, and the came over...Then the REDLINE BOYZ came over. So anyway me and Pat get to workin on putin his subwoofer backin n stuff. And then we reinstalled his Cold Air Intake......That car is runnin like a champ man OK...
